channel.title: I have RuneScape client... but what do I do to it?
channel.description:
[size=15pt][b]I AM NOT SURE IF IT IS REALLY IT, BUT IT HAS THE SAME FILES AS CLIENT AND IT IS CALLED "loader583462365"[/b][/size]
I have the RuneScape client on my desktop now... I'm not sure how to run it. (I'm sure not being able to run it has to do with unpack.class)
I successfully got all the files for the client... I hope... the JAR file's name is "loader583462365".
Now... I have the following .class files... [b]a b c cf hf la loader ri unpack[/b]
In the META-INF folder, I have
[b]Manifest.MF zigbert.RSA zigbert.SF[/b]
[hr]
Now, I'm pretty unknowledged in this... but how would I possibly run it?? I am fine if I have to give it to someone.
